description:
For me and thousands of other fans, grunge music died the day Kurt Cobain left this mortal coil. Everyone is welcome to chat live about Kurt, Nirvana, and any topic that comes to their mind as we approach 24 years since the day grunge died.

Host is MaryGirl Moody.
